 Termination Provisions\n- For cause: 30 days written notice\n- For convenience: 180 days written notice\n- Transition assistance: 90 days minimum\n\nLegal Contact:\n- General Counsel: Amanda Torres\n- Email: atorres@yyj.ca\n- Phone: (250) 555-0199\n\nAppendix reference: See Appendix F for detailed requirements.\nCross-reference: Sections 8, 4, and 6.\n\n\n\n\n--- Page 136 of 136 ---\n\nSECTION 1: 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY (Continued)\n\nAdditional specifications for page 136:\nThe Victoria International Airport (YYJ) is seeking qualified vendors to provide comprehensive parking management services for a period of five (5) years, with two (2) optional one-year extensions. The successful proponent will be responsible for all aspects of parking operations including revenue collection, customer service, facility maintenance, and technology implementation.\n\nKey Dates:\n- RFP Issue Date: January 15, 2025\n- Questions Deadline: February 1, 2025\n- Proposal Due Date: February 28, 2025\n- Contract Award: March 15, 2025\n- Service Commencement: April 1, 2025\n\nContact Information:\n- Procurement Manager: Sarah Johnson\n- Email: sjohnson@yyj.ca\n- Phone: (250) 555-0123\n\nAppendix reference: See Appendix G for detailed requirements.\nCross-reference: Sections 1, 5, and 7.\n"}, :stack "orc-rlm", :timestamp "2026-05-18T15:27:53.10026", :run-id "orc-rlm_01", :model "google/gemini-3-flash-preview"}